              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39877594/" class="">第270页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/60764453/" class=" " title="小太阳">小太阳</a>
                (砍下一根指头，才能把手保住。)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="39877594">
              <div class="short">
                
